M|Abou|tx|**Gino Wickman** is the creator of EOS (Entrepreneurial Operating sy) and founder of EOS Worldwide, a community of certified EOS Implementers who help companies im the sy. Wickman has worked w/ thousands of entrepreneurial leadership teams and has helped them get real traction. *Traction* has sold over 2 million copies and EOS is used by over 250,000 companies worldwide. His work focuses on the practical tools needed to run an entrepreneurial company.